This paper is about machine learning and optimization techniques for structured output prediction. The paper specifically focuses on the max-margin Markov network (\mcn) approach, which is commonly used in areas such as computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
